title: Psycho Fae
description: Fight for survival in the deadly gladiator Fae Games. Jax, Cobra, and Ascher are now my teammates.We're fighting for our lives. And our futures.But nothing is at it seems, and for every secret we uncover, another unfolds.Under the spiteful watch of Xerxes and the evil Fae Queen, it's not clear we're going to survive.Can we work together? Or will we implode?One things for sure, I'm about to uncover my destiny.Power is in my veins. This book 2 of a Trilogy. Psycho Shifters must be read prior to Psycho Fae.
author: Jasmine Mas
